Constant Field Values

goboard

private Board goboard
Qis is an ArrayList of Points whose coordinates are those of the goboard position of the chain's liberties. Liberties of a chain are positions on the goboard that are horizontally or vertically adjacent to the chain and are not occupied by an active stone.
